WEBVTT

00:00:00.128 --> 00:00:01.656
So far, we've spoken about

00:00:01.680 --> 00:00:05.536
all of the wonderful
benefits that sleep provides,

00:00:05.560 --> 00:00:09.040
but how much sleep should
we actually be getting?

00:00:09.064 --> 00:00:11.842
[Sleeping with Science]

00:00:11.866 --> 00:00:13.892
(Music)

00:00:13.916 --> 00:00:16.936
For the average adult,
the current recommendation

00:00:16.960 --> 00:00:20.726
is somewhere between seven to nine
hours of sleep a night.

00:00:20.750 --> 00:00:24.626
